<div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 48px auto 0;">
  <h1>About</h1>
  <p>Claude4Marketing is a blog about marketing strategy and AI tools —
  written, published, and managed almost entirely using Claude Code.</p>
  <p>Every post on this site is drafted by AI, committed to GitHub via
  a terminal conversation, and deployed automatically to Netlify. The
  goal is to explore what's possible when AI handles the publishing
  pipeline — and to share what we learn along the way.</p>
  <p>Topics include AI-assisted content creation, marketing strategy,
  blog infrastructure, and the practical realities of building with
  Claude Code on Windows. The honest version: some things worked
  first time. Some took six attempts. All of it is documented here.</p>
  <p>Built with <a href="https://www.11ty.dev">11ty</a>, hosted on
  <a href="https://netlify.com">Netlify</a>, published with
  <a href="https://claude.ai">Claude</a>.</p>
</div>
